<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08039</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING FOR PUBLIC SALE SHARES IN THE DISPOSITION OF GOVERNMENT CORPORATIONS UNDER THE PRIVATIZATION PROGRAM</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Provides that whenever government owned or controlled corporation or any of their assets are privatized, it shall be through a public offering of not less that 60 % of its shares of stock ; and no person shall own more than 5 % of the  shares of stock of the corporation.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ALEJANO, GARY C.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-08-06</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON GOVERNMENT ENTERPRISES AND PRIVATIZATION ON 2018-08-08</td></tr></table>